          <div class="doc-section">
            <h3 id="content-guidelines" class="doc-h3">Content Guidelines<span class="h3-badge" style="background: rgba(37,99,235,0.1); color: var(--prism-violet);">Recommended</span></h3>
            <div class="do-dont-grid">
              <div class="do-card"><span class="card-label">Do</span>
                <ul>
                  <li>Reflect the real page hierarchy in the trail.</li>
                  <li>Mark only the last item as Current (bold).</li>
                  <li>Keep labels concise and meaningful (e.g. "Settings", "Profile").</li>
                  <li>Use the home icon for app root level entries.</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div class="dont-card"><span class="card-label">Don't</span>
                <ul>
                  <li>Show the user's click history instead of the actual path.</li>
                  <li>Bold or highlight intermediate items.</li>
                  <li>Truncate labels mid-word with ellipsis; abbreviate instead.</li>
                  <li>Place the home icon on every item.</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
